le=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/setSinkId\"><code>setSinkId()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/abort_event\"><code>abort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplay_event\"><code>canplay</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplaythrough_event\"><code>canplaythrough</code></a></li><li><em><code>durationchange</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/emptied_event\"><code>emptied</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ended_event\"><code>ended</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadeddata_event\"><code>loadeddata</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadedmetadata_event\"><code>loadedmetadata</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/pause_event\"><code>pause</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/play_event\"><code>play</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\"><code>playing</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/progress_event\"><code>progress</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ratechange_event\"><code>ratechange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeked_event\"><code>seeked</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeking_event\"><code>seeking</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/stalled_event\"><code>stalled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/suspend_event\"><code>suspend</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/timeupdate_event\"><code>timeupdate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/volumechange_event\"><code>volumechange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/waiting_event\"><code>waiting</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"`durationchange` イベントは、`duration` 属性が更新されたときに発生します。\n\n## 構文\n\nこのイベント名を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> などのメソッドで使用するか、イベントハンドラープロパティを設定するかしてください。\n\n```js\naddEventListener('durationchange', event =&gt; { });\n\nondurationchange = event =&gt; { };\n```\n\n## イベント型\n\n一般の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> です。\n\n## 例\n\nこれらの例では、`HTMLMediaElement` の `durationchange` イベントのイベントリスナーを追加し、そのイベントハンドラがイベントの発生に反応したときにメッセージを投稿します。\n\n`addEventListener()` を使用する場合\n\n```js\nconst video = document.querySelector('video');\n\nvideo.addEventListener('durationchange', (event) =&gt; {\n  console.log('理由はわかりませんが、動画の再生時間が変わりました。');\n});\n```\n\n`ondurationchange` イベントハンドラープロパティを使用する場合\n\n```js\nconst video = document.querySelector('video');\n\nvideo.ondurationchange = (event) =&gt; {\n  console.log('理由はわかりませんが、動画の再生時間が変わりました。');\n};\n```\n\n## 仕様書"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#event-media-durationchange","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLMediaElement.durationchange_event"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"## ブラウザーの互換性"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLMediaElement.durationchange_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/durationchange_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"## 関連イベント\n\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\" title=\"playing\"><code>playing</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/waiting_event\" title=\"waiting\"><code>waiting</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeking_event\" title=\"seeking\"><code>seeking</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeked_event\" title=\"seeked\"><code>seeked</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ended_event\" title=\"ended\"><code>ended</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadedmetadata_event\" title=\"loadedmetadata\"><code>loadedmetadata</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/loadeddata_event\" title=\"loadeddata\"><code>loadeddata</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplay_event\" title=\"canplay\"><code>canplay</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/canplaythrough_event\" title=\"canplaythrough\"><code>canplaythrough</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/durationchange_event\" title=\"durationchange\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>durationchange</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/timeupdate_event\" title=\"timeupdate\"><code>timeupdate</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/play_event\" title=\"play\"><code>play</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/pause_event\" title=\"pause\"><code>pause</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ratechange_event\" title=\"ratechange\"><code>ratechange</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/volumechange_event\" title=\"volumechange\"><code>volumechange</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/suspend_event\" title=\"suspend\"><code>suspend</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/emptied_event\" title=\"emptied\"><code>emptied</code></a> イベント\n- HTMLMediaElement <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/stalled_event\" title=\"stalled\"><code>stalled</code></a> イベント\n\n## 関連情報\n\n- <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLAudioElement\"><code>HTMLAudioElement</code></a>\n- <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a>\n- <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code></a>\n- <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLMediaElement: durationchange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLMediaElement: durationchange","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLMediaElement: durationchange 事件","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/htmlmediaelement/durationchange_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/htmlmediaelement/durationchange_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement","title":"HTMLMediaElement"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/We